Class GeoLocImpl

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.BaseObjectImpl
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.GeoLocImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
SonarObject, GeoLoc, Storable
public class GeoLocImpl extends BaseObjectImpl implements GeoLoc
GeoLoc contains attributes necessary to describe a map location.
Author:
Douglas Lau, Travis Swanston, Michael Janson, John L. Stanley
